            <div>
                <head>Comments</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3c0005-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_004-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2022-08-24T18:33:11.912+09:00">As for Yān and Sòng</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_004-9a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2022-08-24T18:34:20.368+09:00">the reasons why they assassinated their rulers (there)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_004-9a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2022-08-24T18:33:39.058+09:00">were all of this kind. [VK]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_004-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2022-08-29T04:53:28.229+09:00">then in the end he will find himself set aside. [VK]</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_004-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Valerie.Kiel" modified="2022-08-29T04:54:13.236+09:00">(maybe: one obtains them by reflecting on them logically? [VK])</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_015-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-10-01T23:57:05.029+09:00">Note that the topic goes right down to 交援者。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">Generally, what is valued in driving a chariot</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">is that the horse's body is comfortable with the chariot,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">and the driver's mind is in harmony with the horse.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">Only then can one advance swiftly and reach far.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">Now, if Your Lordship lags behind, you wish to catch up with your servant;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-55a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">if you are ahead, you fear being overtaken by your servant.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-56a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-56a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">In leading the way and striving for distance,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-56a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">it is either being ahead or behind.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-56a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">But if the concern for being ahead or behind is entirely focused on the servant,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-56a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">how can the ruler be in harmony with the horse?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-56a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">This is why Your Lordship lags behind."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">Bai Gong Sheng, worried and confused,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">dismissed the court.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">He held his cane upside down and the sharp end pierced his forehead,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">blood flowed to the ground but he did not notice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">The people of Zheng, hearing of this, said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">"If he forgets his forehead,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-57a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">what will he not forget?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-58a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-58a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">Therefore, it is said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-58a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">"The further one goes out,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-58a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">the less one knows."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-58a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">This means that if wisdom encompasses the distant,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-58a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">then what is neglected is in the near.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">Therefore, the sage has no fixed course of action.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">He can combine all wisdom,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">therefore it is said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">"He knows without traveling."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">He can combine all vision,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0005_tls_021-59a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-28T13:20:59.013+09:00">therefore it is said:</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
